FAQs
Why should I choose Serbia for my medical studies?
Serbia offers affordable education, high-quality medical programs, English-taught courses, extensive clinical experience, and a welcoming environment, making it an ideal destination for medical studies.

How can Qadri-International assist me in applying to universities in Serbia?
Qadri-International provides personalized counseling, application assistance, visa support, financial planning, and pre-departure and post-arrival support to ensure a smooth application process and successful transition.

What medical programs are available in Serbia?
Serbian universities offer a range of accredited medical programs, including general medicine, dentistry, and pharmacy, all designed to provide comprehensive education and training in their respective fields.

What support services are available for students in Serbia?
Serbian universities offer a range of support services, including academic advising, career counseling, mental health support, and assistance with accommodation to ensure students have a positive and successful experience.

What is the student life like in Serbia?
Student life in Serbia is vibrant and diverse, with modern campus facilities, a variety of extracurricular activities, and a supportive community that fosters personal and academic growth.

